Text: Australian Energy Risk Australian Energy Risk is approaching I am emailing you with regards to your presentation The deadline date is Monday June If this is going to be a problem please let me know I will be out of the office from Monday until Monday June on which date I will be putting the presentation pack together to send to the printers If your presentation is complete could you please email it to as a powerpoint file ASAP If you have any problems in doing this please do not hesitate to contact me by email or on I will reply to any queries when I return Regards Lucie Deathridge Conference Coordinator Risk Publications Tel
